        {
            "title": "七國集團財長商議稀土等關鍵礦產 如何擺脫對中國的依賴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"七國集團財長商議稀土等關鍵礦產 如何擺脫對中國的依賴\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SMKU9J7pI6_aVgof60q_yA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/aa6bb970-f028-11f0-afdf-2ab3820df414\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">七國集團財長商議稀土等關鍵礦產 如何擺脫對中國的依賴</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%83%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E8%B2%A1%E9%95%B7%E5%95%86%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%80%E5%9C%9F%E7%AD%89%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%A4%A6%E7%94%A2%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%93%BA%E8%84%AB%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B3%B4-235138725.html",
